judi silvano with special guest joe lovano events at stanford judi silvano with special guest joe lovano facebook twitter email print add to calendar judi silvano's extraordinary vocal talents and jazz sensibilities let her assume a unique position in performance she can deliver the tune and she can hang with the horns with an expansive range and uncanny precision judi gives voice to ideas that few singers would ever imagine with a stellar band backing her up this is sure to be one of the highlights of the festival as the jazz & blues report says silvano thinks like a horn player bending and smearing notes even when singing straight ahead standards more than any singer currently on the scene silvano is an artist painting with broadest brush creating colorful harmonies and textures and evoking the best performances from her accompanying musicians when monday july 25 2011 7 30 pm approximate duration of 2 hour s where campbell recital hall 541 lasuen mall stanford ca 94305 map audience faculty staff alumni friends general public students members tags performance music arts sponsor stanford jazz workshop contact 736 0324 info stanfordjazz org admission tickets $28 general $18 students stanford ticket office 650 725 arts 2787 http tickets stanford edu permalink http events stanford edu events 279 27979 more info last modified july 21 2011
